---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="千忆知答 — 知识库问答产品 | 千忆 AI"
  description="千忆知答是千忆 AI 工作室的知识库问答产品，将制度文档、FAQ、培训资料整理成可提问、可追溯来源的智能知识库。"
>
  <!-- ═══ Nav ═══ -->
  <header class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="logo"><span class="logo-mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>千忆 AI</a>
      <button class="nav-toggle" id="nav-toggle" aria-label="菜单" aria-expanded="false"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
      <nav class="nav-links" id="nav-menu">
        <a href="#problems">解决的问题</a>
        <a href="#how">怎么用</a>
        <a href="#faq">常见问题</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">预约演示</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main-content">
    <!-- ═══ 1. Hero ═══ -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <h1 id="hero-headline">千忆知答，让企业资料变成<em>可追溯的答案</em></h1>
          <p class="hero-sub" id="hero-sub">把制度文档、产品手册、客服 FAQ、培训资料整理成可提问的知识库，让团队成员快速获得带来源的可靠答案。</p>
          <div class="hero-actions" id="hero-actions">
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">加微信预约演示</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-ghost">申请体验版本</a>
          </div>
          <p class="hero-note" id="hero-note">资料准备完整后，可快速搭建体验版本</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual" id="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="mock-parallax">
            <div class="product-mock">
            <div class="mock-toolbar"><span class="mock-dot"></span><span class="mock-dot"></span><span class="mock-dot"></span><span class="mock-title">千忆知答</span></div>
            <div class="mock-body">
              <div class="mock-search" id="mock-search" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="点击切换问题示例">
                <span class="mock-search-text" id="mock-search-text">员工手册中关于年假的规定是什么？</span>
                <span class="mock-search-cursor" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-result" id="mock-result">
                <p class="mock-ans" id="mock-ans">根据《员工手册》第三章第 2.4 条：员工入职满一年享有 <strong>5 个工作日</strong> 带薪年假……</p>
                <div class="mock-sources" id="mock-sources"><span class="source-tag">员工手册 v3.2 · 第三章</span><span class="source-tag">考勤制度 v2.1 · 第五条</span></div>
              </div>
              <span class="mock-cycle-hint" id="mock-cycle-hint">点击切换问题</span>
            </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mock-note">知识库问答界面示意</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 2. Problems ═══ -->
    <section class="problems" id="problems" aria-labelledby="problems-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="problems-heading" class="reveal-blur-in">它主要解决这三类问题</h2>
        <div class="problems-row reveal-fade-up reveal-children">
          <div class="prob-item reveal-child">
            <h3>资料分散</h3>
            <p>文档散在共享盘、邮件附件、聊天记录里，每次找资料都像翻箱倒柜。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="prob-item reveal-child">
            <h3>版本混乱</h3>
            <p>制度改了、产品更新了，旧版本还在各个角落，新旧混在一起没人说得清。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="prob-item reveal-child">
            <h3>答案无源</h3>
            <p>老员工离职带走了"谁知道"，新员工只能靠打听——答案有，但找不到源头。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 3. How + Scenarios ═══ -->
    <section class="how-section" id="how" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="how-heading" class="reveal-blur-in">从资料到答案，很简单</h2>
        <div class="how-grid">
          <div class="how-steps reveal-fade-up reveal-children">
            <div class="hs-item reveal-child"><span class="hs-num">1</span><strong>上传资料</strong><span>支持 PDF、Word、Markdown、TXT 等常见格式，可批量导入已有文档库。</span></div>
            <div class="hs-item reveal-child"><span class="hs-num">2</span><strong>直接提问</strong><span>像问同事一样用日常语言提问，一次提问同时检索所有关联文档。</span></div>
            <div class="hs-item reveal-child"><span class="hs-num">3</span><strong>查看来源</strong><span>每条回答标注文档名称和章节位置，点击即可跳转到原文核对。</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="how-scenarios reveal-blur-in">
            <p class="hs-label">适合这些场景</p>
            <ul>
              <li>企业制度查询</li>
              <li>产品手册问答</li>
              <li>客服 FAQ</li>
              <li>新人培训</li>
              <li>售后知识库</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 3.5 Trust ═══ -->
    <section class="trust-section" aria-labelledby="trust-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="trust-heading" class="reveal-blur-in">专注知识库问答的工作室</h2>
        <div class="trust-list reveal-fade-up reveal-children">
          <div class="trust-item reveal-child">
            <h4>聚焦一个方向</h4>
            <p>只做知识库问答这一件事，不做通用 chatbot、不做大而全的平台。你的资料整理和问答效果是我们唯一关心的交付质量。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-item reveal-child">
            <h4>一对一交付</h4>
            <p>每个项目由团队直接对接，从资料评估到体验版本搭建全程跟进。不需要自己看文档、学配置、调参数。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-item reveal-child">
            <h4>先试用，再决定</h4>
            <p>资料准备好之后先搭建体验版本，你和团队实际用起来觉得合适了，再讨论后续。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 4. FAQ ═══ -->
    <section class="faq-section" id="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="faq-heading" class="reveal-blur-in">常见问题</h2>
        <div class="faq-list reveal-fade-up reveal-children">
          <div class="faq-group">
            <h3 class="faq-group-label">产品功能</h3>
            <details class="faq-item reveal-child"><summary>支持哪些文档格式？</summary><p>支持 PDF、Word、Markdown、HTML、TXT 等常见格式，可从本地上传。后续可扩展对接飞书文档、Confluence 等知识源。</p></details>
            <details class="faq-item reveal-child"><summary>回答会显示来源吗？</summary><p>会。每条回答都附有来源引用，包括文档名称和章节位置，点击可跳转到原文核对。</p></details>
            <details class="faq-item reveal-child"><summary>是否支持私有化部署？</summary><p>支持。可部署到私有云或本地服务器，满足对数据安全有更高要求的团队。</p></details>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-group">
            <h3 class="faq-group-label">试用与安全</h3>
            <details class="faq-item reveal-child"><summary>如何预约演示？</summary><p>添加微信 qianyi-ai，备注「千忆演示」，或填写下方表单提交预约信息。</p></details>
            <details class="faq-item reveal-child"><summary>搭建体验版本需要多长时间？</summary><p>资料准备完整的情况下，通常 1-2 个工作日即可搭建出可试用的体验版本。具体时间取决于资料的规模和格式复杂度。</p></details>
            <details class="faq-item reveal-child"><summary>上传的资料安全吗？</summary><p>资料存储在你指定的环境中（本地服务器或私有云），不会用于模型训练。也支持私有化部署，数据完全不出你的网络。</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ 5. Contact ═══ -->
    <section class="contact-section" id="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 id="contact-heading" class="reveal-blur-in">想看看你的资料能不能做成知识库？</h2>
        <p class="contact-desc reveal-blur-in">可以先简单沟通资料类型和使用场景，再判断是否适合搭建体验版本。</p>
        <div class="contact-grid reveal-fade-up reveal-children">
          <div class="contact-wechat reveal-child">
            <span class="cw-label">微信</span>
            <span class="cw-value">qianyi-ai</span>
            <span class="cw-hint">添加时备注「千忆演示」</span>
          </div>
          <form class="contact-form reveal-child" id="contact-form" novalidate>
            <div class="form-row">
              <label for="name">称呼 <span class="label-req" aria-label="必填">*</span></label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="您的称呼" required autocomplete="name" minlength="2" maxlength="30" aria-describedby="name-hint" />
              <span class="form-hint" id="name-hint">如：张经理、李工</span>
              <span class="form-err" id="name-err" role="alert"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
              <label for="team">团队 / 工作室 <span class="label-req" aria-label="必填">*</span></label>
              <input type="text" id="team" name="team" placeholder="团队或工作室名称" required autocomplete="organization" minlength="2" maxlength="50" aria-describedby="team-hint" />
              <span class="form-hint" id="team-hint">你所在的公司或团队名称</span>
              <span class="form-err" id="team-err" role="alert"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
              <label for="contact-info">联系方式 <span class="label-req" aria-label="必填">*</span></label>
              <input type="text" id="contact-info" name="contact" placeholder="微信、邮箱或手机号" required autocomplete="email" minlength="3" maxlength="60" aria-describedby="contact-hint" />
              <span class="form-hint" id="contact-hint">我们会通过此方式与你沟通演示安排</span>
              <span class="form-err" id="contact-err" role="alert"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
              <label for="message">需求说明 <span class="label-opt">选填</span></label>
              <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="2" placeholder="简单描述团队规模和使用场景" maxlength="500" aria-describedby="message-hint"></textarea>
              <span class="form-hint" id="message-hint">告诉我们你的团队规模和想用知识库解决的业务场景</span>
              <span class="form-err" id="message-err" role="alert"></span>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">提交预约</button>
            <p class="form-trust">提交后通常 24 小时内通过微信回复，你的信息仅用于沟通演示安排，不会用于其他用途。</p>
            <div class="form-success" id="form-success" hidden><p>已收到预约信息，也可以直接<strong>添加微信 <span class="wx-hl">qianyi-ai</span></strong> 沟通。</p></div>
            <div class="form-error" id="form-error" hidden><p>提交失败，请重试或直接添加微信 <span class="wx-hl">qianyi-ai</span>。</p></div>
          </form>        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- ═══ Footer ═══ -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-brand"><strong>千忆 AI</strong><span>个人工作室品牌，专注于 AI 知识库与文档问答工具</span></div>
      <nav class="footer-links"><a href="#problems">解决的问题</a><a href="#how">怎么用</a><a href="#faq">常见问题</a><a href="#contact">联系与试用</a></nav>
      <div class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 千忆 AI</div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <button class="back-top" id="back-top" aria-label="回到顶部" hidden>
    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M10 16V4m0 0L5 9m5-5l5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
  </button>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ═══ Shared ═══ */
  .container { max-width: 1160px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--space-8); }
  h2 { font-size: var(--text-h2); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--color-ink); text-align: center; }

  /* ═══ Nav ═══ */
  .nav { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: var(--z-sticky); background: oklch(1 0 0 / 0.88); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .nav-inner { max-width: 1160px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--space-8); height: 52px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
  .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2); text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-ink); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .logo-mark { width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 4px; background: var(--color-primary); }
  .nav-toggle { display: none; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-10); font-size: var(--text-small); }
  .nav-links > a:not(.btn) { color: var(--color-ink); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
  .nav-links > a:not(.btn):hover { color: var(--color-primary); text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-links > a:not(.btn).active { color: var(--color-primary); }

  /* ═══ Buttons ═══ */
  .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--text-small); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 0 var(--space-6); height: 44px; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; transition: background 120ms var(--ease-smooth), border-color 120ms var(--ease-smooth), transform 120ms var(--ease-smooth); }
  .btn:hover { text-decoration: none; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--color-primary); color: var(--color-primary-text); }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--color-primary-hover); color: var(--color-primary-text); }
  .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--color-ink); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--color-primary); color: var(--color-primary); }
  .btn:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }
  .btn-sm { min-height: 44px; height: auto; padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-4); font-size: var(--text-xs); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); }
  .btn-full { width: 100%; }

  /* ═══ 1. Hero ═══ */
  .hero { padding: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) 0 var(--space-12); }
  .hero-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem); align-items: center; }
  .hero-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-5); }
  .hero-text h1 { font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 3.5vw, 2.45rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.35; color: var(--color-ink); }
  .hero-text h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 50ch; }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-4); }
  .hero-note { font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--color-muted); }
  .hero-visual { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2); }
  .product-mock { width: 100%; max-width: 500px; background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); box-shadow: 0 1px 3px oklch(0 0 0 / 0.04), 0 4px 16px oklch(0 0 0 / 0.04); overflow: hidden; }
  .mock-parallax { will-change: transform; }

  /* ── Entrance: pre-entrance hidden state ── */
  .hero-visual.is-pre-entrance { opacity: 0; }
  .hero-visual.is-pre-entrance .product-mock { transform: scale(0.97); filter: blur(6px); opacity: 0; }
  .hero-visual.is-entering .product-mock { transition: opacity 250ms var(--ease-snap), transform 250ms var(--ease-snap), filter 250ms ease-out; opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); filter: blur(0); }
  .hero-visual.is-entering .mock-toolbar .mock-dot { animation: dotPop 200ms ease-out both; }
  .hero-visual.is-entering .mock-toolbar .mock-dot:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 150ms; }
  .hero-visual.is-entering .mock-toolbar .mock-dot:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 180ms; }
  .hero-visual.is-entering .mock-toolbar .mock-dot:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 210ms; }

  .hero-text h1 .hero-word { display: inline-block; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); transition: opacity 220ms var(--ease-snap), transform 220ms var(--ease-snap); }
  .hero-text h1 .hero-word.is-revealed { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  .hero-sub.is-pre-entrance,
  .hero-actions.is-pre-entrance,
  .hero-note.is-pre-entrance { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); }
  .hero-sub.is-entering,
  .hero-actions.is-entering,
  .hero-note.is-entering { transition: opacity 220ms var(--ease-snap), transform 220ms var(--ease-snap); opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  @keyframes dotPop {
    from { transform: scale(0); opacity: 0; }
    60%  { transform: scale(1.25); opacity: 1; }
    to   { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
  }
  .mock-toolbar { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2); padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3); background: var(--color-surface); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .mock-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .mock-dot:nth-child(1) { background: oklch(0.65 0.15 25); }
  .mock-dot:nth-child(2) { background: oklch(0.75 0.12 90); }
  .mock-dot:nth-child(3) { background: oklch(0.55 0.13 140); }
  .mock-title { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-muted); margin-left: var(--space-2); font-weight: 500; }
  .mock-body { padding: var(--space-3); }
  .mock-search { padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4); background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); font-size: var(--text-small); color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 150ms var(--ease-smooth), box-shadow 150ms var(--ease-smooth); user-select: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1px; min-height: 44px; }
.mock-search:hover,
.mock-search:focus-visible { border-color: var(--color-primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px oklch(0.520 0.135 140 / 0.08); outline: none; }
.mock-search-text { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
.mock-search-cursor { display: inline-block; width: 1.5px; height: 1.05em; background: var(--color-primary); vertical-align: text-bottom; opacity: 0; border-radius: 0.5px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.mock-search-cursor.active { opacity: 1; animation: cursorBlink 0.85s step-end infinite; }
.mock-cycle-hint { display: block; text-align: center; font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: var(--space-2); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 220ms var(--ease-smooth); }
.mock-cycle-hint.visible { opacity: 1; }
.mock-ans { transition: opacity 150ms var(--ease-smooth); }
.mock-ans.is-fading { opacity: 0; }
.mock-sources { transition: opacity 150ms var(--ease-smooth); }
.mock-sources.is-hidden { opacity: 0; }
.mock-sources.is-hidden .source-tag { pointer-events: none; }
.source-tag.is-new { animation: sourcePopIn 0.48s cubic-bezier(0.22, 0.61, 0.36, 1) both; }
.source-tag:hover { transform: scale(1.08); box-shadow: 0 0 14px oklch(0.550 0.125 45 / 0.32); }
@keyframes cursorBlink { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0; } }
@keyframes sourcePopIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.75) translateY(5px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1) translateY(0); } }
  .mock-result { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-2); }
  .mock-ans { font-size: var(--text-small); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--color-ink); max-width: none; }
  .mock-sources { display: flex; gap: var(--space-2); flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .source-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: var(--text-xs); font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-accent-text); background: var(--color-accent); padding: 1px var(--space-2); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); transition: transform 120ms var(--ease-smooth), box-shadow 120ms var(--ease-smooth); }
  .source-tag:hover { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 8px oklch(0.550 0.125 45 / 0.25); }
  .mock-note { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-muted); }

  /* ═══ 2. Problems ═══ */
  .problems { padding: 0 0 var(--section-pad); }
  .problems h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-8); }
  .problems-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--space-8); max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .prob-item h3 { font-size: var(--text-h4); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
